promi&s;e
her, That if the Queen had a Son, and &s;he likewi&s;e, he &s;hould
put hers in his place: <HI>What will you lo&s;e by this Sir?</HI> &s;aid &s;he,
<HI>Will it not be your Son that will &s;till Reign, only with this diffe|$ence,
