<P>To return to <HI>C$lderonna:</HI> The King &s;urprized one day the Duke
<HI>de Medi$a</HI> with her, and in the exce&s;s of his Rage, be ran to
<PB N="41" REF="44">
$im with his Poynard in his Hand; he was about to kill him, when
this Woman placed her &s;elf between, telling him, He might &s;trike her
