She put it not off, writing a Letter to the Duke to b$d him Adieu$
And &s;he receiv'd the Veil of a Religio from the Hand of the Apo&s;t$|lick
Nuncio, who became &s;ince <HI>Innocent X.</HI> It is very likely the
